ActCanadian Tourism Commission Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of BHAGWANT S. PARMAR of Brockville, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Tourism Commission, to hold office during pleasure on a part-time basis for a term of three years, in the place of Simon F. Cooper.
